Package: Rnanoflann
Type: Package
Title: Fast Nearest Neighbor using nanoflann library
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2023-10-24
Authors@R: c(
                person("Manos Papadakis", email = "papadakm95@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")), 
                person("Jose Luis Blanco", email = "joseluisblancoc@gmail.com" , role = c("aut","cph")),
                person("Michail Tsagris", role = c("ctb"))
        )
Maintainer: Manos Papadakis <papadakm95@gmail.com>
Copyright: nanoflann library is copyright Jose Luis Blanco. See file COPYRIGHT for details.
Description: Finds the k nearest neighbours for every point in a given dataset using Jose Luis's nanoflan library. There is support for exact searches, fixed radius searches with 'kd' trees and many different distances such as 'Euclidean' or 'Manhattan'. Also, the nanoflann library is exported and ready ot use via the LinkingTo mehcanism.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.11)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
BugReports: https://github.com/ManosPapadakis95/Rnanoflann/issues
URL: https://github.com/ManosPapadakis95/Rnanoflann
